column16: Andrew Benintendi doubles (5) on a ground ball to left fielder Eddie Rosario.   Dustin Pedroia scores.    Xander Bogaerts scores.    Andrew Benintendi to 3rd on the throw.
Xander Bogaerts singles on a ground ball to right fielder Robbie Grossman.   Dustin Pedroia to 3rd.
Dustin Pedroia doubles (3) on a line drive to center fielder Max Kepler.   Sandy Leon scores.    Josh Rutledge scores.    Mookie Betts scores.
Mookie Betts walks.   Sandy Leon to 3rd.    Josh Rutledge to 2nd.
Josh Rutledge reaches on a force attempt, fielding error by shortstop Jorge Polanco.   Sandy Leon to 2nd.
Sandy Leon singles on a ground ball to center fielder Max Kepler.
Chris Young homers (1) on a fly ball to left center field.
Mitch Moreland flies out sharply to center fielder Max Kepler.
Hanley Ramirez grounds out softly, third baseman Miguel Sano to first baseman Kennys Vargas.
Andrew Benintendi flies out to left fielder Eddie Rosario.
Xander Bogaerts strikes out on a foul tip.  Dustin Pedroia steals (1) 2nd base.
